e hundred square foot in size. It used to be a lawn but he turned it into a meadow that is blanketed with wild flowers and exotic flowers. Some of the flower buds haven't opened yet but as the weather gets warmer the flowers open. Even inside his house he has a vase of hydrangea and a few potted plants, some of which are just coming into bloom. Orchids can be cultivated in vases or flower pots. In summer summer flowrs bloom in the meadow. In spring the meadow is covered with lovely spring flowers. In autumn the meadow is blanketed in pretty autumn flowes. In winter it's a mass of beautiful winter flowers. It's an extraordinary garden. He buys his girlfriend a bouquet of red roses, hydrangea and sunflowers every valentine's day. They're lovely cut flowers. Some women seem to bloom in their mid-thirties. For example tracy has bloomed into an utterly beautiful creature. She's an insurance saleswoman who gets a basic salary of eighty thousand eight hundred dollars per month plus a sixteen percent commission on every sale she makes so her job isn't by commission only. So far her.sales have failed to live up to expectations partly because the economy is hardly blooming."},{"pid":"c5b4ef7ce8d3f9875b62e4e47c91fc8dc6ccc2a2","tid":1716342,"uid":338079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bafd897206bfb9757a970713053ef30396ef9b2","tid":1716342,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db35179dc1f6521be721826001d490b12caf92a7","tid":1716342,"uid":141577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"734b0367f8e99f07a9b4fd456c3cae92fd188730","tid":1716342,"uid":70301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"一開Google map睇下個位置喺邊，屌你老味，左右隔籬全撚部都係公屋，送都唔住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl